name: See No Evil (itch) (Vonwarr, Nightstriider, SmallPotato16, Endelle, Space Castle Games)
name_original: See No Evil (itch) (Vonwarr, Nightstriider, SmallPotato16, Endelle, Space Castle Games)
description:
You wake up deep in a dungeon and need to navigate across a gauntlet of traps and tentacles. To preserve your sanity you can close your eyes to avoid the eldritch horrors... but the traps are real, and deadly.

 A player succeeds by reaching the end of the gauntlet, and fails by either dying to a trap or having their sanity drained by a horror.
